# Dataset: silver_deliveries

## Silver Layer Purpose
Validated delivery operations dataset for logistics intelligence and SLA performance monitoring.

---

## Cleaning Rules

| Column | Cleaning Logic |
|---|---|
| Delivery_person_ID | Remove null values |
| Delivery_person_Ratings | Validate rating range |
| Vehicle Type | Standardize categories |
| Latitude/Longitude | Validate coordinate ranges |
| Time_taken(min) | Remove unrealistic durations |

---

## Validation Framework

| Validation Category | Rule |
|---|---|
| Delivery Validation | Delivery time must be positive |
| Coordinate Validation | Latitude/Longitude valid |
| Rating Validation | Ratings between 1–5 |
| Vehicle Validation | Approved vehicle categories only |
| Duplicate Validation | Delivery IDs unique |

